<item>
            <title>[WICKET-4579] PackageTextTemplate misses locale, style and variation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-4579</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because of PackageTextTemplate calls IResourceStream.locate(clazz, path) it is currently not possible to set locale, style and variation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12558790">WICKET-4579</key>
            <summary>PackageTextTemplate misses locale, style and variation</summary>
